 ('1', '1', 'en', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-02-27 15:05:18', '2017-02-27 15:05:18', 'd48ca024-d652-4438-a3dc-962962d1f6c3'),
 ('2', '2', 'en', 'Welcome to Victoriafans!', '<p>It’s true, this site doesn’t have a whole lot of content yet, but don’t worry. Our web developers have just installed the CMS, and they’re setting things up for the content editors this very moment. Soon Victoriafans will be an oasis of fresh perspectives, sharp analyses, and astute opinions that will keep you coming back again and again.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-02-27 15:05:21', '2017-03-02 17:00:07', 'dad32780-537e-4516-b84f-11244b4888f3'),
 ('4', '4', 'en', 'General Ventilation', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p>This is General Ventilation, Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipisicing elit. Ipsam minus totam in explicabo voluptate quas consequatur mollitia, ducimus adipisci aliquid animi vero veritatis fugit! Enim commodi optio, itaque nisi fugit!</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-02-27 15:10:36', '2017-07-24 16:20:00', 'bc052df8-01ea-4e6a-abd0-020f9b1eabc9'),
 ('5', '5', 'en', 'Fume Control', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p>There are a number of factors to take into account when installing a fume control system: The type of substance in the contaminated area, flammability or combustibility, required airflow, pressure, resistance and of course the mounting position and space available.  Our advisory team are always happy to chat through your particular circumstance and ensure you order the correct product.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-02-27 15:10:49', '2017-10-03 08:48:26', '230df4f4-69d8-4aa4-9295-4d030d7a75e9'),
 ('6', '6', 'en', 'Emergency Smoke Extraction', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p>In the event of a fire in densely populated buildings such as Hospitals, Stores, Sports Centres and Shopping Malls, it is essential that adequate emergency smoke ventilation is provided.  This not only keeps escapes routes clear but also minimises damage to buildings and contents and assists the Fire Service in fighting fire.</p>\n<p>The type of fan can be used as part of a Roof Extract unit incorporating a Victoria fabricated steel Vertical Jet Roof Extract Cowl.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-02-27 15:11:01', '2017-10-03 08:47:02', '9448227d-ccd3-444f-95fe-b694d9c55e45'),
 ('7', '7', 'en', ' Roof Extract Fans', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p>As their suggests this range of fans is used on flat or sloping roofs and is suitable for exhausting warm and contaminated air up to a maximum ambient temperatures of 60°C using an axial or propeller type fan upto 600°C using axials or bifurcated fans.</p>\n<p>Air volumes from 0.5 – 50m³/sec</p>\n<p>Both LOW PROFILE and VERTICAL JET models can be fitted with single or three phase motor in TEFC or flameproof enclosures.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-02-27 15:11:11', '2017-10-03 08:39:00', 'aa12e500-e50d-4db9-9162-be5313669573'),
 ('16', '17', 'en', 'Axial Flow Fans', NULL, '<p>Our Axial Fans can be supplied as both cased and plate mounted versions. These fans are suitable for most applications including general ventilation for large, medium and small industrial spaces.  The size of space and purpose will determine which variant and size of fan is most appropriate to your specific requirement.  Our experts are on hand to assist you with choosing the correct fan.</p>', 'All Long and Short cased fans can be supplied with 304 or 316 Stainless Steel Casings', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '', '', '', '', '', '2017-02-27 16:02:49', '2018-01-10 09:32:14', 'a04c4c22-b132-4391-83c8-3ee736a6d647'),
 ('17', '18', 'en', 'Plate Mounted Axial', NULL, '<p>This is all about the plate mounted axial fan</p>', NULL, '<p>Plate Mounted Axial fans are designed for Clean Air Supply and extraction of poor quality air. By adding a vertical jet or low profile cowl, these fans serve as effective roof extract units. See Cowel options.</p>', 'Wall or roof mounting where ducting is not required.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '', '', '', '', '', '2017-02-27 16:03:13', '2017-11-24 13:53:29', '7b15f80a-3636-4dcb-ae81-7385b3ae81b0'),
 ('18', '19', 'en', 'Bifurcated Fans', NULL, '<p>Bifurcated fans are used to exhaust a wide variety of hot gases, paint fumes, smoke, steam and dust in suspension.</p>', 'For the foodstuffs and chemical industries these fans can be constructed from stainless steel of aluminium at competitive cost.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '', '', '', '', '', '2017-02-27 16:07:43', '2017-11-24 09:33:00', 'bf7d1aa7-647f-4330-aeed-664b9b96ede4'),
 ('19', '20', 'en', 'Centrifugal Fans', NULL, '<p>Praesent non elit nec sem interdum suscipit quis imperdiet felis. Praesent nulla ligula, consectetur sit amet tortor commodo, tristique viverra ex. Pellentesque laoreet erat sit amet sagittis tempor.</p>', 'Since forward curved and paddle blade fans have overloading power characteristics it is important that the static selection pressure is achieved.  Any reduction in the requirements could easily overload the motor.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '', '', '', '', '', '2017-02-27 16:08:02', '2017-11-24 15:02:49', '0ff74193-578b-44d5-992a-b97b9f8bb30e'),
 ('20', '21', 'en', 'Flameproof Fans for hazardous areas, zones 1 & 2', NULL, '<p>All Axial and Centrifugal fans can be fabricated to suite hazardous areas, Zone 1 and Zone 2.  Please contact our sales team for specific information.</p>', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '', '', '', '', '', '2017-02-27 16:08:22', '2018-01-10 09:47:14', 'd557dd43-ea08-4191-8080-54d751ec3b91'),
